title: Solitaire 3D 1.4
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Solitaire gets a 3D face-lift. The application contains all your
favorite solitaire games, including Klondike, Spider, Golf,
FreeCell, and Pyramid. Select one of seven preset boards to play
on or easily create your own custom 3D boards. It comes with
fully customizable 3D views, sounds, and 3D animation effects.
Version 1.4 features an improved graphics system, 3D card
models, and seven new solitaire games.
